# About page
msgid "关于 Hermes Agent 插件"
msgstr "About Hermes Agent Plugin"

msgid "本地 AI 助手 — 直接在 iStoreOS 路由器上运行，通过 LLM API 控制路由器系统。"
msgstr "Local AI assistant - runs directly on iStoreOS router, controls router system via LLM API."

